{"tid":2071633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班垃圾英文都講唔撚到，仲想BNO平權？","createTime":"2020-06-20T03:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T12:20:30.000Z","uid":287461,"like":48,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9c17d1dd94f6c5ea460ec6e26a62030293967c","tid":2071633,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 標題黨呃你地入黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係想叫大家學好英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國安法中明目張膽咁加入「國家安全教育」，擺明係想洗下一代嘅腦，加強佢地對中國嘅身分認同，令佢地成為小粉蛆。<br />\n<br />\n卡繆話，&ldquo;I live in my own language&rdquo; 。<br />\n香港係港英統治下，粵語同英文都係我地嘅own language。<br />\n你想唔想你地嘅下一代話：「我黃皮膚，黑眼睛，我講中國話，所以我是中國人／廣東省人！」？<br />\n香港唔似台灣，台灣雖然講華語，而且英文水平都唔係好好，但佢地台灣冇國民洗腦教育，唔會被中共滲透，小朋友個腦唔會被洗成粉蛆。<br />\n就算奶共如新加坡，佢地都會話自己係Singaporean而唔係中國人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">英文，就係其中一個區分香港人同大陸人嘅重要指標<br />\n就算中共嘅洗腦幾強勁都好，只要我地緊抱住英文，身分認同就唔會係問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n而且香港咁細嘅地方，免不了要依附其他勢力，你地嘅語言，就係一張選票，選擇自己要投入中國圈子，定Anglosphere。<br />\n移民，係用腳投票；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">語言，係用舌頭投票</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知我講嘅野夠唔夠plausible，夠唔夠persuasive，有冇道理，就算覺得唔啱聽，都唔該，學好英文。<br />\n（twitter都可以學英文，所以勤力啲啦）<br />\n（聽講睇<span style=\"color: violet;\">peppa pig</span>學British English好有用，又簡單又地道，冇咩英文底嘅非常推薦，其實幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n（英文有咁上下水平嘅睇多啲外國新聞／外國youtube channel）<br />\n<br />\n廣東話最重要，但英文一樣重要。我希望後代能講一口純正嘅香港話／粵語嘅同時，都講到純正嘅英文。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">粵語英語，缺一不可！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nbtw連登仔唔該唔好成日笑人講英文啦，香港國際城市，講英文有咩問題？識講粵語&amp;英文，就係香港人嘅身份證。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住，香港，係屬於國際嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊努力。"},{"pid":"afe39a6e1f38c1ea7c4f5bf00881c93bd5f53890","tid":2071633,"uid":287461,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"負皮條友係唔係冇睇內文"},{"pid":"354ca48788497396eaeee20f041d3efb0db940a8","tid":2071633,"uid":35430,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"本身入黎想屌鳩你架喇，但見你咁有誠意<br />\n算啦"},{"pid":"f3bcf929e4ab7bf61797a65b7683eb780fc66d03","tid":2071633,"uid":239942,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"真，自己會考得3,跟住renew bno同自己講<br />\n如果要對得住個英國籍，英文唔可以差<br />\n最後英文考左全8 而家移左去澳洲"},{"pid":"f2782c6767e16b8301c363ff24006fe91311e5ed","tid":2071633,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9c42257871223da06f02976785f10e2ba0afb3","tid":2071633,"uid":315988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"I go to school by bus"},{"pid":"75399e3cc309ffd26ad925cb1e4c00b16eb94082","tid":2071633,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9c42257871223da06f02976785f10e2ba0afb3","tid":2071633,"uid":315988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"I go to school by bus"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f45790bbac7b1d7dec8d37903c32c442c4365bb","tid":2071633,"uid":315988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75399e3cc309ffd26ad925cb1e4c00b16eb94082","tid":2071633,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9c42257871223da06f02976785f10e2ba0afb3","tid":2071633,"uid":315988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"I go to school by bus"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,